    <item>
      <title>美国就业数据火爆后新兴市场货币暴跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-02/china-stocks-lag-emerging-market-peers-by-most-in-11-months</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美国就业报告井喷，引发人们对美联储将推迟降息至 3 月甚至 5 月之后的担忧，新兴市场货币周五暴跌。土耳其央行行长辞职后，土耳其里拉当天晚些时候下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-02/china-stocks-lag-emerging-market-peers-by-most-in-11-months</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 02 Feb 2024 11:47:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着加沙谈判将原油价格推低至关键价格水平以下，石油跌幅加深</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-01/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-feb-2</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于暂停以色列与哈马斯战争的谈判降低了原油的地缘政治风险溢价，油价暴跌，在大宗商品跌破关键技术水平后，跌势加速。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-01/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-feb-2</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Feb 2024 23:44:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
